          <h2 class="section-title">Four steps. Zero memory code.</h2>
          <p class="section-desc">Vitamem manages the full memory lifecycle behind the scenes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hiw-grid">
          <div class="hiw-step">
            <div class="hiw-num">1</div>
            <div class="hiw-label">CHAT</div>
            <div class="hiw-desc">User talks to your AI. You write zero memory code — just call <code>chatWithUser()</code>.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="hiw-step">
            <div class="hiw-num">2</div>
            <div class="hiw-label">REST</div>
            <div class="hiw-desc">Conversation goes quiet. Vitamem notices automatically via <code>sweepThreads()</code>.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="hiw-step">
            <div class="hiw-num">3</div>
            <div class="hiw-label">REMEMBER</div>
            <div class="hiw-desc">Key facts are extracted, embedded, and deduplicated — one batch, not fifty calls.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="hiw-step">
            <div class="hiw-num">4</div>
            <div class="hiw-label">RECALL</div>
            <div class="hiw-desc">Next session, relevant memories appear in context. Pinned facts always included.</div>
